ent \n*[[Ravinder Bhalla]], New Jersey politician and [[Hoboken, New Jersey|Hoboken]] mayor elect.\n*[[Gurbir Grewal]], 61st Attorney General of New Jersey.\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Athletes==\n\n===Athletics===\n[[File:Milkha Singh.jpg|130px|thumb|[[Milkha Singh]]]]\n*[[Milkha Singh]],<ref>[http://www.sikh-history.com/sikhhist/personalities/sports/milkha.html Sikh Sports personality Flying Sikh Milkha Singh] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225164938/http://www.sikh-history.com/sikhhist/personalities/sports/milkha.html |date=2015-02-25 }}. Sikh-history.com. Retrieved on 2010-12-14.</ref><ref>[http://www.mapsofindia.com/who-is-who/sports/milkha-singh.html Milkha Singh]. Mapsofindia.com; retrieved 2010-12-14.</ref><ref>[http://www.rediff.com/sports/2000/sep/08milka.htm Olympics Special: Milkha Singh on the race of his life]. Rediff.com; retrieved 2010-12-14.</ref><ref>[http://www.sadapunjab.com/cv/Literature_On_Punjab/PUNJAB/Milkha_Singh_The_Flying_Sikh/index0.html Milkha Singh The Flying Sikh] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100324114916/http://www.sadapunjab.com/cv/Literature_On_Punjab/PUNJAB/Milkha_Singh_The_Flying_Sikh/index0.html |date=2010-03-24 }}. Sadapunjab.com; retrieved 2010-12-14.</ref> \n*[[Gurbachan Singh Randhawa]]\n*[[Kamaljeet Sandhu]]\n*[[Fauja Singh]],<ref>[http://www.sikhtimes.com/bios_041904a.html Biographies \u2013 Fauja Singh: \"I Run While Talking to God\"]. The Sikh Times (2004-04-19); retrieved 2010-12-14.</ref> a 100-year-old marathon runner\n\n===Basketball===\n*[[Sim Bhullar]], Canadian professional basketball player<ref>{{cite news|last1=Magagnini|first1=Stephen|title=Region's Sikhs rally behind Kings rookie Sim Bhullar|url=http://www.sacbee.com/sports/nba/sacramento-kings/article17482079.html|accessdate=2 June 2016|work=[[Sacramento Bee]]|date=April 5, 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Satnam Singh Bhamara]]\n\n===Boxing===\n*[[Andrew Kooner|Andrew Singh Kooner]], current Bantamweight Champion of Canada\n*[[Akaash Bhatia]], 